00:46.263 --> 00:48.165
right with him. Somebody says, well, if they find 
out about that in Washington, they'll transfer

00:48.226 --> 00:54.754
you clear out of this country. Well, we said, we've 
been here too long anyway. We started that

00:58.807 --> 01:03.473
practice, and one of us needed to get out of the 
service to get out there to it. So I thought, well,

01:04.674 --> 01:09.260
if I can get that job as state veterinarian, I'll be 
